headline: S&P 500 Q2 2025 Buybacks Declines 20% Amidst Uncertainty to $235 Billion From Q1 2025's Record $293 Billion; Q3 2025 Expenditures Expected to Increase Back to Near Record Levels
summary: S&P Dow Jones Indices (S&P DJI) today announced the preliminary S&P 500® stock buybacks or share repurchases data for Q2 2025.

headline: CARFAX: Fall Is Most Dangerous Season For Car Accidents in the U.S.
summary: Next week, tens of millions of drivers will hit the roads during what CARFAX data shows is themost dangerous season to drive: Fall. While many may assume Winter would bring the most crashes, CARFAX analysis found that in 39 states, Fall accounted for the highest percentage of accidents compared to all other seasons.
